# Offline Zero-Downtime CI/CD Simulation

## 🎯 Objective
Demonstrate a **CI/CD pipeline with zero-downtime deployment** without relying on Docker or Kubernetes.

## 💡 Project Overview
- Simulates multiple instances of an application (replicas)
- Shows rolling update from v1 → v2
- Fully offline, reproducible in any terminal
- Suitable for resume or portfolio to show CI/CD knowledge

## 🛠️ Steps
1. Run the simulation script:
```bash
./simulate_zero_downtime.sh
